{"tid":2329414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"最後在2月9日失蹤，據悉當時官方破門而入。陳、方兩人到現時仍然下落不明","createTime":"2020-12-17T08:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T09:47:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4a03caaf72551cb86281714c5de20969f68a3a5","tid":2329414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:25:47.000Z","msg":"最後在2月9日失蹤，據悉當時官方破門而入。陳、方兩人到現時仍然下落不明<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://https.appledaily.com/china/20201217/Q2ZZZ6K7TRHW7KSCLFLXYP64UQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhttps.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201217%2FQ2ZZZ6K7TRHW7KSCLFLXYP64UQ%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28fGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=5562e221\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhttps.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201217%2FQ2ZZZ6K7TRHW7KSCLFLXYP64UQ%2F&h=9af42010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https.appledaily.com/china/20201217/Q2ZZZ6K7TRHW7KSCLFLXYP64UQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n未包括失蹤記者 外交部避而不談<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1xzV-yWl0Kk4879R-PnBoL9qwT4=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SW2ANOYAXVBYDMWYA7RWGZDGOI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1xzV-yWl0Kk4879R-PnBoL9qwT4%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSW2ANOYAXVBYDMWYA7RWGZDGOI.jpg&h=59524580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■採訪武漢肺炎令中國公民記者身陷囹圄。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次保護記者協會的2020年中國監禁名單，沒有收錄一些失蹤的公民記者，如律師陳秋實及武漢公民記者方斌。陳、方兩人同樣在今年二月初於武漢失蹤，至今仍然下落不明。至於近日被捕的彭博記者范若伊則相信數據未更新至12月中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳秋實訪武漢收警告電話<br />\n<br />\n陳秋實是1月24日抵達武漢，到達時中國官員才剛宣佈武漢封城。隨後近兩周，陳抵達多間武漢醫院、殯儀館、居民區，採訪了多位當地百姓，並將影片發佈在互聯網上。陳秋實多次在影片中透露，國家機器向他逼近，收到很多警告電話，他在1月30日影片曾說：「我前面是病毒，後面是中國法律，只要我活在這座城市，我會繼續進行我的報道！」接着他哭着說：「我連死都不怕，我怕你共產黨嗎？」該影片在YouTube點擊高達230萬，最後在2月6日失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n方斌是武漢居民，他在2月1日拍攝武漢醫院，其間嘆氣說：「這麼多呀。」他數了一下，五個、六個、七個、八個屍袋。「這麽多的人就這麽死了。」影片令人質疑官方有意隱瞞死亡數字，官方在2月2日便上門沒收了他的電腦，還盤問了他拍攝屍袋錄像的情況，<span class=\"orange\">最後在2月9日失蹤，據悉當時官方破門而入。陳、方兩人到現時仍然下落不明</span>，外媒多次向外交部、駐英大使劉曉明查詢近況，但外交部一是推說不了解情況，一是答非所問，指摘美國政府亦曾驅逐60名中國記者。"},{"pid":"54f174580642904c1047f697a43e1277d450af51","tid":2329414,"uid":241628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n秋實真係由手足變左鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948e2bb506c98818f197ce0bdd789247321fb44a","tid":2329414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"多因揭露武肺真相遭清算  中國今年囚117記者冠全球<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2329323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2329323</a>"},{"pid":"520759c99fa2191767d5f29163556753c0825897","tid":2329414,"uid":275161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:03:30.000Z","msg":"中國真係好撚垃圾 <br />\n推"},{"pid":"37aee0b98e3acb8837071b6b6a2421a62f81057b","tid":2329414,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:10:35.000Z","msg":"希望佢地安好 係大陸講真話既代價實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc76c47167d6353ed7dc99ae2d09f774e080418","tid":2329414,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"陳秋實明明知名度咁高<br />\n係法律界新星<br />\n失左踪都無人問過究竟<br />\n垃圾虫國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb00a6ef6dec1b7a439448c9f82805720d784dff","tid":2329414,"uid":72630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5bc76c47167d6353ed7dc99ae2d09f774e080418","tid":2329414,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:12:40.000Z","msg":"陳秋實明明知名度咁高<br />\n係法律界新星<br />\n失左踪都無人問過究竟<br />\n垃圾虫國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"